I was thinking on my run today that the big difference between us and our
competitors is that we're diagnostic instead of proscriptive. Imagine if
gAnalytics had started out by saying "we know what will make you the best
possible used tires store. Or beany-babies fan site. And we'll tell you
exactly how to measure getting there."

Instead they just measured success towards whatever the client designated.
That's our differentiator; as we exit Covid everyone is going to have
disruption at top of mind; we provide a means for you to quickly and
elegantly maneuver your company towards whatever success looks like,
whatever the market conditions.

No?

